<bdy>

The <b>2001 Humber Refinery explosion</b> was a major incident at the then <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../479/3717479.xml">
Conoco</link>-owned <plant wordnetid="103956922" confidence="0.8">
<refinery wordnetid="104068441" confidence="0.8">
